column2: SELECT TOP # s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, cast (str (p.u - p.g, #, #) as float) as ugModelColor, cast (str (p.g - p.r, #, #) as float) as grModelColor, cast (str (p.r - p.i, #, #) as float) as riModelColor, cast (str (p.i - p.z, #, #) as float) as izModelColor, p.score as score FROM ..SpecObj as s JOIN ..Galaxy AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq (#, #, #) AS b ON b.SpecobjID = S.SpecobjID JOIN Galaxy AS p ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.zWarning = # AND (p.u - p.g) > # AND (p.u - p.g) < # AND (p.flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags (#) ) > #)
